OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFrance backs bill to ban   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdisposable vapes           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The French parliament has voted        
OL,6, unanimously to ban single-use          
OL,7, e-cigarettes, known locally as "puffs",
OL,8, amid health and environmental concerns.
OL,10,FIt still needs backing from France's   
OL,11,FSenate and clearance from the EU       
OL,12,FCommission before it becomes law.      
OL,14,FIf both approve the bill, the          
OL,15,Fgovernment said it hopes the ban will  
OL,16,Fbe effective by September 2024.        
OL,18,FSeveral other countries in Europe,     
OL,19,Fincluding the UK, Ireland, and Germany 
OL,20,Fare considering similar measures.      
